sources.description:
Two weeks before graduation, Lucy, a devout Catholic schoolgirl, learns her best friend just had an abortion. This rattles her world, and in order to balance her internal sense of moral injustice, Lucy dangerously plots to kill the doctor who performed her best friend's procedure. She becomes entangled in romantic deception, academic trouble, and police suspicion as she struggles to execute her plan.

2021.  Stars: Ana Mackenzie, Ken Ashton, Keana Marie
